---
import IndexedTitle from "../../components/IndexedTitle.astro";
---

<section
  class="py-32 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-0"
  id="about"
>
  <div>
    <IndexedTitle index="01">About Me</IndexedTitle>
    <p class="mb-4 text-dim">
      I build AI systems for real people. Tools smart enough to matter and
      simple enough to actually get used. What I make is built to hold up at
      scale, with reliable pipelines and outputs that behave predictably in
      production.
    </p>
    <p class="text-dim">
      I work as an R&D engineer, so I stay close to what is happening in AI
      research and make a point of bringing what is actually useful into the
      work I ship. That includes solid experience with speech and audio models,
      fine-tuning for low-resource languages, and pushing the same thinking into
      image and multimodal work.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="img-container w-[250px] lg:w-[300px]">
      <img loading="lazy" src="/profile.jpg" alt="developer avatar" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  img {
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .img-container {
    border-radius: 5px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 250ms ease;
  }

  .img-container::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    background-color: #3afc7e;
    opacity: 20%;
    transition: opacity 250ms ease;
  }

  .img-container:hover::before {
    opacity: 0%;
  }
  .img-container::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 10px;
    left: 10px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -10;
    border: 2px solid #3afc7e;
    border-radius: 5px;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: transform 250ms ease;
  }

  .img-container:hover::after {
    transform: translate(10px, 10px);
  }

  .img-container:hover {
    transform: translate(-5px, -5px);
  }
</style>
